title: Nami needs more skins

embed.title: Jellyfish Nami (With picture!) - League of Legends Community
embed.description: Years of conversation fill a ton of digital pages, and we've kept all of it accessible to browse or copy over. Whether you're looking for reveal articles for older champions, or the first time that Rammus rolled into an "OK" thread, or anything in between, you can find it here.

body:
Hello!

I've found this post,it's an interesting "request" for a jellifish nami skin.
it's very well made and nice...it could really be an interesting skin...i'd totally instabuy it,considering both koi and river spirits in game are a lot worse compared to splash arts.

Here's the link to the original post here on lol forums:
